@Login @Login_passportos
Feature: PassportOS Login

  Background: 
    Given User is on the PassportOS login page with title of "Login_Page_Title"

  @Tc_01 @passportos-neg
  Scenario Outline: Verify user fails to login with invalid or missing credentials
    Then User enters "<Email>" in the "username" field
    Then User enters "<Password>" in the "password" field
    Then User clicks on the "Continue" button
    Then User should see login error message "<ErrorMessage>"

    Examples: 
      | Email        | Password        | ErrorMessage                  |
      | invalidEmail | invalidPassword | Wrong email or password       |
      | validEmail   | invalidPassword | Wrong email or password       |
      | invalidEmail | validPassword   | Wrong email or password       |
      | EMPTY        | invalidPassword | Please enter an email address |
      | invalidEmail | EMPTY           | Please enter an email address |
      | EMPTY        | EMPTY           | Please enter an email address |

  @Tc_02 @passportos-pos
  Scenario: Verify user logs in successfully with valid credentials
    Then User enters "validEmail" in the "username" field
    Then User enters "validPassword" in the "password" field
    Then User clicks on the "Continue" button
    And User is redirected to Dashboard page with title "Dashboard_Page_Title"
